{"title":"Open positions","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"Open positions","toc":false,"format":{"html":{"theme":"vigilab.scss","css":"styles/positions.css"}}},"headingText":"We are hiring!","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n::: {.positions-container}\n\n\n<p style= \"margin: 0.5rem 0;\n  margin-top: 3rem;\n  margin-left: 0vw;\n  margin-right: 10vw;\n  font-size: 1.30rem; \n  font-family: 'Lucida Sans', 'Lucida Sans Regular', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n  font-weight: 800;\n  color: #05014a;\n  text-align: center;\"> \n  Our team is growing! We have two open positions to be filled as soon as possible. Details below...</p> <br> <br>\n\n{{< include resources/positions/2025-08-22-postdoc.qmd >}}\n{{< include resources/positions/2025-08-22-phd.qmd >}}\n\n##\n\n\n<p style= \"margin: 0.5rem 0;\n  margin-top: 3rem;\n  margin-left: 0vw;\n  margin-right: 10vw;\n  font-size: 1.20rem; \n  font-family: 'Lucida Sans', 'Lucida Sans Regular', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n  color: #05014a;\n  text-align: center;\"> \n  Apart from open calls for funded positions, we are always excited to discuss potential doctoral/post-doctoral positions through external fellowships. <br> <br>\n  As a growing lab there are always positions for **masters and undergraduate** students to contribute to our team. <br><br>\n  Please do not hesitate to reach out at [vignesh.kannan@polytechnique.edu](vignesh.kannan@polytechnique.edu) if you are interested in working with us. </p>\n\n:::\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n::: {.positions-container}\n\n## We are hiring!\n\n<p style= \"margin: 0.5rem 0;\n  margin-top: 3rem;\n  margin-left: 0vw;\n  margin-right: 10vw;\n  font-size: 1.30rem; \n  font-family: 'Lucida Sans', 'Lucida Sans Regular', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n  font-weight: 800;\n  color: #05014a;\n  text-align: center;\"> \n  Our team is growing! We have two open positions to be filled as soon as possible. Details below...</p> <br> <br>\n\n{{< include resources/positions/2025-08-22-postdoc.qmd >}}\n{{< include resources/positions/2025-08-22-phd.qmd >}}\n\n##\n\n\n<p style= \"margin: 0.5rem 0;\n  margin-top: 3rem;\n  margin-left: 0vw;\n  margin-right: 10vw;\n  font-size: 1.20rem; \n  font-family: 'Lucida Sans', 'Lucida Sans Regular', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n  color: #05014a;\n  text-align: center;\"> \n  Apart from open calls for funded positions, we are always excited to discuss potential doctoral/post-doctoral positions through external fellowships. <br> <br>\n  As a growing lab there are always positions for **masters and undergraduate** students to contribute to our team. <br><br>\n  Please do not hesitate to reach out at [vignesh.kannan@polytechnique.edu](vignesh.kannan@polytechnique.edu) if you are interested in working with us. </p>\n\n:::\n"},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":null,"freeze":false,"echo":true,"output":true,"warning":true,"include":true,"keep-md":false,"keep-ipynb":false,"ipynb":null,"enabled":null,"daemon":null,"daemon-restart":false,"debug":false,"ipynb-filters":[],"ipynb-shell-interactivity":null,"plotly-connected":true,"engine":"markdown"},"render":{"keep-tex":false,"keep-typ":false,"keep-source":false,"keep-hidden":false,"prefer-html":false,"output-divs":true,"output-ext":"html","fig-align":"default","fig-pos":null,"fig-env":null,"code-fold":"none","code-overflow":"scroll","code-link":false,"code-line-numbers":false,"code-tools":false,"tbl-colwidths":"auto","merge-includes":true,"inline-includes":false,"preserve-yaml":false,"latex-auto-mk":true,"latex-auto-install":true,"latex-clean":true,"latex-min-runs":1,"latex-max-runs":10,"latex-makeindex":"makeindex","latex-makeindex-opts":[